{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019-05-25/what-we-can-do-to-prevent-cancer","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"c817c91a-cd13-51cc-80cb-bc792b68e3e0","html":"<p>  世界卫生组织研究报告显示：至少三分之一的癌症可以得到预防。作为普通人，从哪些方面思考关于癌症的预防?生活中哪些小事做到后，能降低患癌症的风险呢？以下为我最近几个月查询癌症相关资料后的总结：</p>\n<p>  第一，基因。</p>\n<p>  第二，环境。</p>\n<p>  第三，个人。</p>\n<p>  第四，化学预防。</p>\n<p><figure><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/203d3/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"    \"\n        title=\"    \"\n        src=\"/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/5a190/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/772e8/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png 200w,\n/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/e17e5/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png 400w,\n/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/5a190/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png 800w,\n/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/c1b63/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png 1200w,\n/static/716f43f7de12c08d6bada7afa0504d41/203d3/%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87.png 1322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">如果希望存在</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>  关于基因，如果家族有两位以上患同一种癌症，那么请关注是否有遗传或基因缺陷，如果有条件，可以提前做基因检测，具体咨询医生。</p>\n<p>  关于环境，请自查自己的生活、工作环境（灰尘、辐射等）是否与环境污染，是否会引起职业病？注意：已证明二手烟能使不吸烟者罹患肺癌，紫外线能导致皮肤癌。</p>\n<p>  关于个人，可以从心理、运动、体重、饮食等方面调节。</p>\n<p>  心理作用，是一项暂时无法用指标来衡量对人体影响的因素，保持乐观的心态，说得简单，但真正做到乐观，难。特别事情发生在自己身上时，乐观更是难能可贵。</p>\n<p>  如果可以，尽量做到每周至少三次运动，每次不少于三十分钟。让自己的身体和头脑都保持灵活的状态，注意保持健康的体重。若出现不明原因的体重下降，请尽快就医检查原因。</p>\n<p>  饮食多样化，减少红肉摄入，注重蔬菜水果，戒酒。</p>\n<p>  关于化学预防，请咨询专业医生。</p>","fields":{"slug":"2019-05-25/what-we-can-do-to-prevent-cancer","prefix":"2019-05-25"},"frontmatter":{"title":"预防癌症，我们能做哪些?","author":"文:Jane","category":["thought"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/1be3b13c4711fe5b7398d60ccba17b66/9dc27/cancer.jpg"}}}}},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"2019-10-11/i-am-back","prefix":"2019-10-11"},"frontmatter":{"title":"I am back"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"2019-05-20/the-last-days","prefix":"2019-05-20"},"frontmatter":{"title":"感恩母爱，思念我娘 —— 母亲在世的最后72天"}},"authornote":{"id":"86780e07-dd43-5b96-827f-d5867264385a","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"2019-05-25/what-we-can-do-to-prevent-cancer","total":57,"prev":"2019-10-11/i-am-back","next":"2019-05-20/the-last-days"}}}